{"tid":2246348,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國有教師被斬首　疑兇曾犯罪但未被列入反恐監察名單","createTime":"2020-10-17T03:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T06:01:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a1409c8079dc5f631b608832e92adbbd3dbc331e","tid":2246348,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:41:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555246-20201017.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555246-20201017.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao%2B9tl09raJ%2B2zMWOssuGUT0%3D&h=272bf094\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555246-20201017.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bbd5928f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555246-20201017.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n法國一名教師被斬首，疑兇被警方擊斃。總統馬克龍譴責事件是恐襲，呼籲國民團結，共同抵抗極端主義。<br />\n<br />\n案發在巴黎市郊一間學校附近，當地星期五下午，疑兇持刀在街上，襲擊一名中學教師。疑兇隨後在鄰近城市，因拒捕被警方擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n報道指疑兇是一名18歲生於俄羅斯莫斯科的車臣男子，有犯罪紀錄，但未被法國反恐部門列入監察名單。報道又指遇害教師於本月較早時候，曾在有關言論自由及當年《查理周刊》襲擊案的課堂上，向學生展示《查理周刊》中諷刺伊斯蘭先知穆罕默德的漫畫，但有在課堂前預告教材可能構成冒犯，邀請穆斯林學生暫時離開。"},{"pid":"f7a6e60d7406b1eed729e59db63f3c699dfaa0c7","tid":2246348,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c6cfcaecb7735dc156df7a9493336f0db0f649","tid":2246348,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:01:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}